lead_paragraph: The Dallas Cowboys cleared a big obstacle thanks to Ezekiel Elliott's hurdle of a defensive back in one of the more impressive and perfectly executed decisions of Week 3.

headline.print_headline: Elliott, Cowboys Clear Hurdles in Week 3
